---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Intellectual Property — Rentar Fuel Catalyst | Rentar"
  description="Rentar intellectual property: international patent portfolio, proprietary catalyst formulation, manufacturing processes, trademarks, and commercial licensing rights."
>
  <section class="hero" style="min-height:35vh;">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="hero-tag">Intellectual Property</p>
      <h1 style="font-size:2.6rem;">Protected Technology</h1>
      <p>The Rentar Fuel Catalyst is protected by an international portfolio of patents covering the technology, formulation, manufacturing, and commercial application.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="manifesto-block">
        <p>The Rentar Fuel Catalyst represents more than two decades of engineering, field deployment, and intellectual property development. The technology is protected through an international patent portfolio and associated proprietary manufacturing processes developed for heavy duty diesel applications.</p>

        <p>Rentar Environmental Solutions is the exclusive worldwide commercial rights holder for the Rentar Fuel Catalyst, including the exclusive authority to manufacture, market, distribute, license, sell, and deploy the technology throughout industrial and commercial markets.</p>

        <p class="highlight-label" style="font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);font-size:1.15rem;margin-top:32px;">Intellectual Property Portfolio</p>
        <ul style="list-style:none; padding-left:0; margin-bottom:24px;">
          <li style="padding:6px 0; color:var(--gray-text);">International patent portfolio</li>
          <li style="padding:6px 0; color:var(--gray-text);">Proprietary catalyst formulation</li>
          <li style="padding:6px 0; color:var(--gray-text);">Manufacturing processes</li>
          <li style="padding:6px 0; color:var(--gray-text);">Commercial licensing rights</li>
          <li style="padding:6px 0; color:var(--gray-text);">Application engineering</li>
          <li style="padding:6px 0; color:var(--gray-text);">Product branding and trademarks</li>
          <li style="padding:6px 0; color:var(--gray-text);">Technical documentation and deployment methodologies</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="highlight-label" style="font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);font-size:1.15rem;margin-top:32px;">Unauthorized Use</p>
        <p>No individual, company, reseller, manufacturer, representative, or third party is authorized to manufacture, market, distribute, license, sell, or commercialize the Rentar Fuel Catalyst unless expressly authorized in writing by Rentar Environmental Solutions. Claims of authorization should be independently verified with Rentar prior to purchase.</p>

        <p class="highlight-label" style="font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);font-size:1.15rem;margin-top:32px;">Report Unauthorized Representation</p>
        <p>If you believe a company or individual is falsely claiming to be an authorized Rentar distributor or is marketing, selling, or representing Rentar products without authorization, please contact us immediately at <a href="mailto:info@rentar.com?subject=Unauthorized%20Rentar%20Reseller%20Report" style="color:var(--orange);">info@rentar.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
